  * Add support for quantal in lxc-ubuntu and lxc-ubuntucloud
  * Drop support for maverick in lxc-ubuntu and lxc-ubuntucloud

 -- Stéphane Graber <stgraber@ubuntu.com>  Wed, 02 May 2012 21:28:11 -0400

